OL,3,CHeat pump launched with monthly
OL,4,Cpayment plan in latest bid to take on
OL,5,Cgas
OL,7,FA Swedish company is launching a heat
OL,8,Fpump paid for in monthly instalments
OL,9,Fin the latest push to get UK
OL,10,Fhouseholds to switch away from gas
OL,11,Fboilers.
OL,13,FAira is offering new air source heat
OL,14,Fpumps, operated via a smart app, with
OL,15,Fmonthly payment plan to avoid upfront
OL,16,Fcosts and a 15-year "comfort
OL,17,Fguarantee" in which it takes
OL,18,Fresponsibility for maintenance and
OL,19,Fkeeping the house cosy.
