OL,7,FThe firm's UK chief executive Daniel
OL,8,FSarefjord said "the boiler is the
OL,9,Fenemy" as he said residential heating
OL,10,Fwas responsible for 16% of the UK's
OL,11,Fcarbon emissions.
OL,13,FThe Government has set a target for
OL,14,F600,000 heat pumps to be installed
OL,15,Feach year by 2028 as part of efforts
OL,16,Fto decarbonise heating.
