OL,7,FIt is providing a grant ` increased
OL,8,Flast year to #7,500 ` for an air
OL,9,Fsource pump to reduce the high upfront
OL,10,Fcosts of the clean tech and encourage
OL,11,Ftake-up, and some energy companies are
OL,12,Foffering their customers the
OL,13,Fopportunity to move to heat pumps.
OL,15,FBut industry experts have warned that
OL,16,Finstallations will have to increase by
OL,17,Fmore than 10-fold in the next few
OL,18,Fyears to hit that target.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/7
