OL,7,FA "clean heat market mechanism" which
OL,8,Frequires boiler manufacturers to sell
OL,9,Fa certain proportion of heat pumps, to
OL,10,Fboost the sector is also due to come
OL,11,Fin, but there have been reports it
OL,12,Fcould be scrapped.
OL,14,FAnd high electricity costs compared to
OL,15,Fgas in the UK mean that, although
OL,16,Felectric heat pumps are around four
OL,17,Ftimes more efficient than a boiler,
OL,18,Fthe savings are not as high as they
OL,19,Fcould be for households making the
OL,20,Fswitch.
