OL,7,FMr Sarefjord said in the UK the Aira
OL,8,Fsystem would overall still save 25% on
OL,9,Fheating compared to a boiler ` where
OL,10,Fcosts mount up through servicing and
OL,11,Fmaintenance ` and that could rise to
OL,12,F50% when used alongside clean tech
OL,13,Fsuch as solar panels.
OL,15,FThe overall cost is around #3,000 to
OL,16,F#7,000, after the Government grant,
OL,17,Fwhich is split into 12 interest-free
OL,18,Fmonthly payments.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
