OL,7,FTo further encourage customers, the
OL,8,Fcompany is looking to provide a
OL,9,Ffinancing solution that would spread
OL,10,Fthe payments over a decade, as it
OL,11,Falready offers in Italy, though it
OL,12,Fsaid UK regulations were more
OL,13,Fcomplicated.
OL,15,FMr Sarefjord said Aira was an end-to-
OL,16,Fend company, designing its products
OL,17,Fwith Scandinavian style, manufacturing
OL,18,Fthe heat pumps, employing and training
OL,19,Fstaff to install, maintain and service
OL,20,Fthem, and providing finance to make
OL,21,Fthe products affordable.
